Subject: [PATCH 48/84] config-parser: Support loading multiple configs

Try loading .ini configs under "<config>.d/".

Tested with:
/etc/xdg/weston/weston.ini.d/99-pixman.ini
[core]
use-pixman=true

Signed-off-by: Jeffy Chen <jeffy.chen@rock-chips.com>
---
